      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The reclamation forces In the ir-\nrigation congress achieved a COM\nplete victory this afternoon when\nformer Governor Pardee OF Califor-\nmia was elected permanent chair\nman Of the resolutions committee.\n\n\nThe choice Is made all the more\nsignificant by the fact that Frank\nn. Short, also Of California, and\nrecognized as power trust attor-\nney, seconded the nomination.\n\n\nWith The Press story Of the\nMontana grab before the delegates\nthere was nothing else to do."
